{
    "version": 5,
    "bundle": "Y64OWO4PQLYFWQ7GZW2BRW2FMYCM7IWX",
    "type": "story",
    "storyId": "830091002",
    "title": "もしもその身が自由なら",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "図書室で調べものをしていると、\r\n偶然ある記事の見出しが\n目に飛び込んできた。",
            "enText": "While doing research in the library, \nthe headline of an article happened \nto catch my eye.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 95,
            "pathId": 9147464209310046352,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "『――シリウスシンボリ、出走回避か』",
            "enText": "\"―Sirius symboli avoids running?\"",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 68,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "（これは……？）",
                    "enText": "(Is this ……?)",
                    "nextBlock": 3
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1896998709079385957,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "記事を手に取り、読み込む。\r\nそこにはトレセン学園入学以前の\nシリウスシンボリのことが書かれていた。",
            "enText": "Pick up the article and read it. There, I \nread about Sirius symboli before she entered \nTressen Academy. Sirius symboli before she \nentered the training academy.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 110,
            "pathId": -4175659857399197371,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "『彼女の父はURAの重鎮で熱心な教育者。\r\n一方、彼女の所属する育成クラブもまた\n優秀なウマ娘を数多く輩出している』",
            "enText": "'Her father is a heavyweight in the URA and a \ndedicated educator. On the other hand, the \ntraining club to which she belongs also has \nproduced a number of excellent horsegirl.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 120,
            "pathId": 4658975203091296397,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "『そんな双方がシリウスシンボリの教育方針\r\nをめぐって対立した。今回の出走回避には、\nその影響が表れているようだ』",
            "enText": "The two sides were at loggerheads over Sirius \nSimboli's education policy. The reason for \nthe avoidance of the race this time The \navoidance of the race this time seems to be a \nreflection of that.",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 119,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "（……出走回避、か）",
                    "enText": "(…… avoid running, huh?)",
                    "nextBlock": 6
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1598854278195744739,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "……何を熱心に読んでるんだ？",
            "enText": "…… What are you eagerly reading?",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 63,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "うわあ！？",
                    "enText": "Wow!",
                    "nextBlock": 7
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 47,
                    "pathId": 5272688541929402388
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 74,
                    "pathId": -5280201497543931356
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3670893619409469053,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "オイオイ、んなビビんなよ。\r\nそんなに刺激的な本を読んでたのか？　ん？",
            "enText": "Oi oi oi, don't be so scared. Have you been \nreading something that exciting? Hmm?",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 90,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "いや、別に――",
                    "enText": "No, I don't―",
                    "nextBlock": 8
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 118,
                    "pathId": 5525470981532874838
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 101,
                    "pathId": -3694934522010616010
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8572955805703634811,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスの後輩",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……っ、ぐすっ……！　シリウス先輩……っ！",
            "enText": "…… gosh ……! Sirius Senpai ……!",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 72,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 83,
                    "pathId": -1041314614477703151
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 83,
                    "pathId": -3530816048739075646
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -975959579221820267,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "……何だ？",
            "enText": "…… What is it?",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 51,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 14,
                    "pathId": 3824329954897817404
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 62,
                    "pathId": 6699836240059255865
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8430501451847104132,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスの後輩",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "あの……あのっ――\r\n私っ……、どうしたら……っ！！",
            "enText": "Um…… um― I…… how can I…… how can I ……!",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 78,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -5300391885593925358
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -3004806478941997120
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 715567892750821009,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "その時、泣きながら駆け寄ってきたのは\r\nシリウスシンボリの後輩らしきウマ娘だった。",
            "enText": "At that moment, a horsegirl who seemed \nto be Sirius symboli's junior came \nrunning up to her crying.",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 98,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 143,
                    "pathId": -7619291173284810444
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 148,
                    "pathId": 696784254655025019
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1551150651045617684,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "後輩の話はこうだった。彼女の母は\r\nもともと病気がちだったが、とうとう倒れ、\n入院することになってしまったという。",
            "enText": "The story of my junior colleague goes like \nthis. Her mother, who had always been ill, \nfinally collapsed hospitalized.",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 119,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 14,
                    "pathId": 939720311263685260
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 14,
                    "pathId": -3140869171566297417
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1919440428656089810,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスの後輩",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "病院は実家のほうなので、遠くって……\r\n移動だけで半日はかかっちゃって……っ。",
            "enText": "The hospital is far away from my \nparents' house, so it took me half \na day…… just to get there.",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 95,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 156,
                    "pathId": 4307877685913658911
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 155,
                    "pathId": 2218038926583693161
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 958615482593899198,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスの後輩",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "私……明日レースなのに……っ！",
            "enText": "I'm…… racing tomorrow and I'm ……!",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 64,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 75,
                    "pathId": 937301326042244864
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 75,
                    "pathId": -2020851309617997320
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 973620643984302537,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "……そうか。\r\nで、お前の意志は？",
            "enText": "…… I see. So what's your will?",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 67,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": -175901482374134226
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": 2886231747223576085
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7797335040957189488,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスの後輩",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "それは……――",
            "enText": "It can be found at ……―",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 54,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 65,
                    "pathId": 4789001666319091944
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 65,
                    "pathId": 8108754175036955949
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2830219040841017035,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスの後輩",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "レースには出たいけど、お見舞いにも\r\n行きたい……こんな状態でレースに\n出たって仕方ないし……っ。",
            "enText": "I want to go to the race, but I also \nwant to go to the hospital to visit \nmy sick family. It's no use to go to \na race in this condition. ……",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 108,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 119,
                    "pathId": -3921339927416537263
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 119,
                    "pathId": 5669107176555369030
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7209849513955788622,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "…………。",
            "enText": "…………",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 51,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 14,
                    "pathId": -3601486413902922589
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 62,
                    "pathId": -172144872488345195
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7488628167903505209,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "『二兎を追う者は一兎をも得ず』って\r\nことわざがあるだろ。",
            "enText": "You know the saying, \"She who runs after two \nhares will catch neither.",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 82,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 14,
                    "pathId": 8111688786650123022
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 14,
                    "pathId": -9088669995240278981
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2114483748752189645,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "だが一方で『一挙両得』『一石二鳥』\r\nなんて言葉も存在している。\n意味がわからないと思わねぇか？",
            "enText": "But on the other hand, there are also words \nsuch as \"one stone pays for both\" and \"two \nbirds with one stone. Don't you think it \ndoesn't make sense?",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 107,
            "pathId": 256537846211127660,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "要するに、だ。\r\n――どっちでもいい。お前が決めろ。",
            "enText": "In short. ―It doesn't matter \nwhich one. You decide.",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 78,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 121,
                    "pathId": 4249201440380928794
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 128,
                    "pathId": 299251815088822567
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8089129929367709032,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "欲しいなら奪え。貪欲になれ。両方を追えよ。",
            "enText": "If you want it, take it. \nBe greedy. Go after both.",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 72,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 56,
                    "pathId": 3669261253398279477
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 83,
                    "pathId": -1834089854899621849
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5840467351322233273,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "そうなりてぇから、私のもとへ来たんだろ？",
            "enText": "That's why you came to me, right?",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 55,
                    "pathId": 8968433843062586314
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": 1018866589653876160
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1087389178425438505,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスの後輩",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "…………。",
            "enText": "…………",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 51,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 62,
                    "pathId": 6003368333554908192
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 62,
                    "pathId": 7988987945452234887
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8540378702283432092,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "テメェ1人の力で足りねぇってんなら、\r\n貸してやる。",
            "enText": "If you're not strong enough on your own, I'll \nlend you a hand.",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 78,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 36,
                    "pathId": 8431688096771572387
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -838843738023527296
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6867151033338194498,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "レースの後、母親に会いに行きてえ、\r\nだがレース後の手続きをしてる暇がねえ、\n急な外泊が必要だってんなら言え。",
            "enText": "You want to go see your mother after \nthe race, but you don't have time to \ngo through the post-race formalities. \nIf you need to stay out overnight on \nshort notice, let me know.",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 116,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 106,
                    "pathId": 1211862874633950028
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 127,
                    "pathId": -1877707729440756882
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7749315172117559992,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "くだらねぇ後処理なんぞ、\r\n適当に誤魔化しといてやるよ。",
            "enText": "I'll just let the stupid post-processing \nstuff slide.",
            "nextBlock": 28,
            "origClipLength": 81,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 39,
                    "pathId": 4740215644376940914
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 92,
                    "pathId": -49293274264119502
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8673948019822322136,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスの後輩",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……！　本当、ですか……？",
            "enText": "……! Really, is it ……?",
            "nextBlock": 29,
            "origClipLength": 61,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 72,
                    "pathId": -4829583277060486948
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 72,
                    "pathId": 820745679160905050
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5093713248502097143,
            "blockIdx": 28
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "ハッ、私が1度言ったことを覆すと思うか？",
            "enText": "Ha, you think I'm going to \noverrule what I said once?",
            "nextBlock": 30,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 54,
                    "pathId": 7540839088972552999
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": -4519848645371945424
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8243058650692950204,
            "blockIdx": 29
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスの後輩",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……っ、いいえ……っ！\r\nもう1度、ちゃんと考えてみます……。\nそれでお母さんとも話してみます……っ！",
            "enText": "…… no ……! I'll think it over again and…… \nAnd I'll talk to my mom about it, too……!",
            "nextBlock": 31,
            "origClipLength": 111,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 122,
                    "pathId": -5162578137849875618
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 122,
                    "pathId": 2915317827481695201
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3118059415513040622,
            "blockIdx": 30
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "シリウスシンボリの後輩は、\r\n吹っ切れたような顔でその場を後にした。",
            "enText": "Sirius Simboli's junior left the place with a \nblown-out look on her face.",
            "nextBlock": 32,
            "origClipLength": 89,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "面倒見がいいんだな",
                    "enText": "You take good care of them.",
                    "nextBlock": 32
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "面倒見がいいんだね",
                    "enText": "You take good care of them.",
                    "nextBlock": 32
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": 4372531832773179427
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 100,
                    "pathId": -3628032629756322716
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7537290899766866942,
            "blockIdx": 31
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "別に。アイツらが勝手に寄ってくるだけ。\r\n私は適当に答えてるだけだ。",
            "enText": "Nothing. They just come up to me on their \nown. I'm just answering as I see fit.",
            "nextBlock": 33,
            "origClipLength": 89,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 58,
                    "pathId": 6177107499298404959
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 100,
                    "pathId": 7040005688743452050
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6890947028162357476,
            "blockIdx": 32
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "それに、どうせツケを払うなら\r\n何事も自分で決めたほうがいいだろ？",
            "enText": "Besides, if you're going to foot the bill \nanyway, you might as well make your own \ndecisions about everything, right?",
            "nextBlock": 34,
            "origClipLength": 88,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 59,
                    "pathId": 1075930671628273324
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 99,
                    "pathId": -7789100477910281252
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 128299722765848311,
            "blockIdx": 33
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "ガキじゃねぇんだ。\r\nアイツならきっと、自分で選べるだろうよ。",
            "enText": "She's not a kid. I'm sure she \ncan make her own choices.",
            "nextBlock": 35,
            "origClipLength": 120,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "（……！）",
                    "enText": "(……!)",
                    "nextBlock": 35
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": 202835809514425467
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": 1909400326919130349
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4855244562145743067,
            "blockIdx": 34
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "今の言葉を聞き、\r\n先ほど読んだ記事の内容が頭をかすめた。",
            "enText": "Hearing what you just said, the contents of \nthe article I just read came to my mind.",
            "nextBlock": 36,
            "origClipLength": 82,
            "pathId": -5944800267467165412,
            "blockIdx": 35
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……あくまで過去の事だが、出走回避の\r\n決定は当時の彼女の意思ではなかったように\n思えた。なら、彼女にとって――",
            "enText": "…… is only a thing of the past, but it did \nnot seem to be her intention at the time of \nthe decision to avoid the race. It seemed to \nme that the decision not to run was not her \ndecision at the time. Then, for her―",
            "nextBlock": 37,
            "origClipLength": 118,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "（『自分で選ぶ』ということの価値は……）",
                    "enText": "(The value of 'choosing for yourself' \ncan be found at ……)",
                    "nextBlock": 37
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8385858037984032121,
            "blockIdx": 36
